snippet.title: Official SuperCTF Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Official Launch Trailer for SuperCTF!
Play SuperCTF! - https://www.superctf.com

Come join us on Wednesdays at 7pm PST and 7pm BST to play SuperCTF! Link to discord below.

Trailer made by the amazingly talented and handsome Teho.
Huge thanks to Pridehobe, Aircu, and JamJar for making this possible.
Fewer thanks to Kabbage.

Join Our Discord - https://discord.gg/mhJRNMc

Music - Mammagammaguchi by EX-LYD
